        <div class="text-center mb-5">
            <h2 class="fw-bold text-dark display-6">Industries & Services We Provide</h2>
            <p class="text-muted mt-3 mx-auto lead" style="max-width: 720px;">
                Each solution is designed to optimize operations, efficiency, and decision-making for your business or organization.
            </p>
        </div>

        <div class="row g-4">
            <div class="col-md-6 col-lg-4">
                <div class="p-4 text-center bg-white border-0 shadow rounded-4 h-100 transition-all hover-shadow">
                    <h5 class="fw-bold text-dark mb-3">Commercial & Industrial</h5>
                    <p class="text-muted small mb-0">
                        Energy efficiency, power audits, and system optimization to enhance operational performance for commercial and industrial facilities.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="col-md-6 col-lg-4">
                <div class="p-4 text-center bg-white border-0 shadow rounded-4 h-100 transition-all hover-shadow">
                    <h5 class="fw-bold text-dark mb-3">Government</h5>
                    <p class="text-muted small mb-0">
                        Utility planning, public infrastructure reliability solutions, and support for effective governance and service delivery.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="col-md-6 col-lg-4">
                <div class="p-4 text-center bg-white border-0 shadow rounded-4 h-100 transition-all hover-shadow">
                    <h5 class="fw-bold text-dark mb-3">Investment Stakeholders</h5>
                    <p class="text-muted small mb-0">
                        Technical due-diligence, feasibility analysis, and advisory services for investors and financial entities evaluating energy and infrastructure projects.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="col-md-6 col-lg-4">
                <div class="p-4 text-center bg-white border-0 shadow rounded-4 h-100 transition-all hover-shadow">
                    <h5 class="fw-bold text-dark mb-3">Data Centers & Large Loads</h5>
                    <p class="text-muted small mb-0">
                        Redundant, high-availability power architecture for data centers and industrial-scale loads to ensure continuous operations.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="col-md-6 col-lg-4">
                <div class="p-4 text-center bg-white border-0 shadow rounded-4 h-100 transition-all hover-shadow">
                    <h5 class="fw-bold text-dark mb-3">Power Delivery</h5>
                    <p class="text-muted small mb-0">
                        Transmission and distribution grid analysis, optimization, and solutions for reliable power delivery.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="col-md-6 col-lg-4">
                <div class="p-4 text-center bg-white border-0 shadow rounded-4 h-100 transition-all hover-shadow">
                    <h5 class="fw-bold text-dark mb-3">Power Generation</h5>
                    <p class="text-muted small mb-0">
                        Performance studies and optimization for thermal, hydro, and renewable power generation facilities.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="col-md-6 col-lg-4">
                <div class="p-4 text-center bg-white border-0 shadow rounded-4 h-100 transition-all hover-shadow">
                    <h5 class="fw-bold text-dark mb-3">Renewable Energy Integration</h5>
                    <p class="text-muted small mb-0">
                        Advanced analysis and solutions for integrating solar, wind, and other renewable systems into existing energy networks.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>
